The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 PCB contracts

Karachi: The PCB on Wednesday announced a performance-related central contract for its 20 players with an increase of 25 per cent. 

Every win in a Test or a ODI against England, West Indies (at home) and South Africa (away series) will make each player richer by Rs 200,000 ($3,333). (PTI) 




